OL,3,CMinimum wage rises on the Isle of Man
OL,5,FThe Manx Government has increased the
OL,6,Fminimum wage on the Isle of Man.
OL,8,FThe rate has now risen from #12.25 to
OL,9,F#13.46, while the youth rate has risen
OL,10,Fto #10.76. Both rises are effective
OL,11,Ffrom the 1 April 2026.
OL,13,FMinisters say a new funding formula
OL,14,Faims to find the "right balance"
OL,15,Fbetween supporting workers and not
OL,16,Fincreasing the burden on businesses.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
