OL,3,CMinimum wage rises on the Isle of Man
OL,5,FTim Johnston MHK, Minister for
OL,6,FEnterprise commented: "The Minimum
OL,7,FWage proposal is Government delivering
OL,8,Fon the longstanding commitment from
OL,9,Fthe Select Policy Committee.
OL,11,F"The original ambition was parity with
OL,12,Fthe Living Wage in 2025, and after a
OL,13,Fcomprehensive review and recognising
OL,14,Fthe challenges faced over the years,
OL,15,Fwe have developed a more sustainable
OL,16,Fapproach.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
