OL,3,CMinimum wage rises on the Isle of Man
OL,5,F"This new rate represents a fair and
OL,6,Fconsidered step forward, based on a
OL,7,Fnew methodology that is clear,
OL,8,Fevidence-based and rooted in the real
OL,9,Fstatus of the Island's economy, while
OL,10,Falso delivering on the will of
OL,11,FTynwald."
OL,13,F"Throughout this process, achieving
OL,14,Fthe right balance has been key `
OL,15,Fsupporting both our workforce with
OL,16,Ffair pay with the need to not
OL,17,Foverburden our business community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
