OL,3,CMinimum wage rises on the Isle of Man
OL,5,F"However, we do recognise that
OL,6,Fincreases in Minimum Wage rates will
OL,7,Fcreate challenges for businesses,
OL,8,Fparticularly smaller employers.
OL,10,F"The Department for Enterprise offers
OL,11,Fa range of support through the
OL,12,FEnterprise Support Schemes and is also
OL,13,Fbuilding on wider concerted efforts to
OL,14,Fincrease footfall and demand, through
OL,15,Fa range of initiatives set out in the
OL,16,Flocal Economy Strategy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
