OL,3,CMinimum wage rises on the Isle of Man
OL,5,FDr Alex Allinson MHK, Treasury
OL,6,FMinister added: "Our aim was to create
OL,7,Fa stable, transparent framework for
OL,8,Fsetting the Minimum Wage that gives
OL,9,Fcertainty to both employers and
OL,10,Femployees, and we welcomed Tynwald's
OL,11,Fsupport in July in agreeing a clear
OL,12,Fway forward.
OL,14,F"While we are mindful that any
OL,15,Fincrease must be manageable for
OL,16,Fbusinesses, fair pay is fundamental to
OL,17,Fa strong and inclusive economy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
