OL,3,CMinimum wage rises on the Isle of Man
OL,5,F"By linking the Minimum Wage to median
OL,6,Fearnings, we are ensuring that wage
OL,7,Fgrowth remains connected to the
OL,8,FIsland's wider economic performance."
